{"tid":2336198,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國目標2025年完善「人工影響天氣工作體系」 《彭博》專欄作家:「這看起來像武器」","createTime":"2020-12-22T12:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:37:19.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"645ac7c2787eae13c4013ed89ea6d9559fa0c5b1","tid":2336198,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:05:08.000Z","msg":"中國國務院12月發布「關於推進人工影響天氣工作高質量發展的意見」，目標是在2025年完善該國「人工影響天氣工作體系」；《彭博》專文評論指出，「這看起來像武器」，中國此舉已引發其他亞洲國家關切。<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院官網發布的文件內容指稱：「到2025年，形成組織完善、服務精細、保障有力的人工影響天氣工作體系，基礎研究和關鍵技術研發取得重要突破，現代化水平和精細化服務能力穩步提升，安全風險綜合防範能力明顯增強，體制機制和政策環境更加優化，人工增雨（雪）作業影響面積達到550萬平方公里以上，人工防雹作業保護面積達到58萬平方公里以上。到2035年，推動我國人工影響天氣業務、科技、服務能力達到世界先進水平。」<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》刊出資訊專欄作家明斯特（Adam Minter）的評論，他認為，中國的天氣調控方案領先世界，讓乾旱地區多降雨、會毀田的冰雹少發生、在國家重要活動時多放晴，但中國的態度已不再這麼客氣了，這次宣布的「意見」還要將造雨能力覆蓋全中國近60%的地區，細節雖然還不清楚，但已令人愈來愈擔心此類技術的潛在軍事用途。<br />\n<br />\n明斯特指出，其他亞洲國家也越來越關注此事，中國可能破壞千年來養活這些國家百姓的季風和規律降雨，雖然操縱天氣的科學仍待探究，但憂慮絕非杞人憂天，對於水情吃緊的地區而言，這種技術小則帶來外交壓力，大則如同武器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3388266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388266&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpNekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=1cbed6e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388266&h=d73b3cd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3388266</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-12-17/has-china-mastered-weather-modification-should-we-worry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2020-12-17%2Fhas-china-mastered-weather-modification-should-we-worry&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpNekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=b86803f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-12-17/has-china-mastered-weather-modification-should-we-worry</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HD5gWv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHD5gWv2.png&h=cd0b1ffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5909471d075026f5d8edd26f95fabc5a50d4080a","tid":2336198,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2015/01/23/150123114328_11.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F640%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2015%2F01%2F23%2F150123114328_11.gif&h=2a6f0348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nX哥（陰陰嘴偷笑）：葡你阿嬤"},{"pid":"a629ced70213f21b8843e4cced074a5ba4c199c2","tid":2336198,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"台灣都2021 都未控制到啦，咁多嘢控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca57142bf1f43f1307e636e8aec65c0f745ff750","tid":2336198,"uid":362754,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"人地美國一早有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba2516c916714dfb2f1fd38a22298bbbbebf8ff","tid":2336198,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"有人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8f44a7079006271a6366a45f25aa477298277a","tid":2336198,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"放心 天氣控制只會搞自己國人民  其他國家既佢唔敢搞"},{"pid":"7eb71db5e157802582c5fb37a55daa307a9d4e6e","tid":2336198,"uid":45857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:28:58.000Z","msg":"證明紅軍工程師已經佔領咗盟軍基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=